{"tid":309561,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 性感內衣女倒掛半空中","createTime":"2017-07-05T06:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T15:03:43.000Z","uid":22136,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea2016c54945116d81bfdfc692eb9c77938cd60","tid":309561,"uid":22136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"大陸遼寧一處民宅外近日出現一個奇異的景象，一名僅穿的紅色內衣、內褲的女子吊掛在窗外的電線上面，且身體還是呈現頭下腳上的詭異姿勢，附近民眾見狀後全都相當緊張，趕緊找來消防隊協助，費了一番工夫才將女子從高空中救下。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/141947_2fea609234c6e5e466a61569bfaac210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F141947_2fea609234c6e5e466a61569bfaac210.jpg&h=e0847fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，該名女子被吊掛的位置約有3層樓高，現場目擊者指出，當時女子原本在5樓擦窗戶，沒想到擦到一半卻突然重心不穩，整個人就這樣掉出窗戶外，還好公寓外牆邊還有老舊的電線尚未拆除，女子的腿剛好勾住才沒有直接墜落地面。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/142624_46d72d2ded1872b67fcf807d94e0a7be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F142624_46d72d2ded1872b67fcf807d94e0a7be.jpg&h=d3951b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防員到場後，先在女子下方架設梯子，接著派員將女子接入2樓窗口，前後花費約10分鐘。然而，由於女子掛在上頭時一動也不動，讓現場民眾相當驚慌，對此，消防員則指出，女子沒有動靜是因為她嚇暈了，「現在已經清醒，沒甚麼大礙。」<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:<a href=\"http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/world/%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%80%92%E6%8E%9B%E5%8D%8A%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD-%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8B%E8%85%B3%E4%B8%8A%E5%9A%87%E5%A3%9E%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE/ar-BBDK8Rq?li=AAazejl&amp;ocid=spartanntp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2580%2592%25E6%258E%259B%25E5%258D%258A%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%259A%2587%25E5%25A3%259E%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%2Far-BBDK8Rq%3Fli%3DAAazejl%26ocid%3Dspartanntp&d=ZETiPhJ0t%2B%2BGroWVQ6EUKb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2a074d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/world/%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%80%92%E6%8E%9B%E5%8D%8A%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD-%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8B%E8%85%B3%E4%B8%8A%E5%9A%87%E5%A3%9E%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE/ar-BBDK8Rq?li=AAazejl&amp;ocid=spartanntp</a>"},{"pid":"5c2c0b7898de7753bae205fc49d28c5f7a5b4e0d","tid":309561,"uid":22136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c29ebc2ac15f997bf27155f34433c4bf24eb05","tid":309561,"uid":114483,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"諗起隔離瑜珈個post..."},{"pid":"0cec620773767a76dcc1b5855a10aaf3bffac6b9","tid":309561,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"仲諗住入黎睇假人/吹氣公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be865b4088c6fd7dd49843cc18fe04bb8e8187c","tid":309561,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2716323d188bb550cd4796e55487c43f45f4f833","tid":309561,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住入黎睇假人/吹氣公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd82e3804f449c180774980822fe2fbedfee11","tid":309561,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住入黎睇假人/吹氣公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame"},{"pid":"237b0fa7c034c3c9ffa